# SYNTHETIC_FIXTURE_PLAN.md

## Purpose

Plan synthetic fixture categories for {{ project.name }}.

This optional template describes fixture categories only. It does not create fixture data files, runtime tests, source code, live configuration, or device integration.

## Scope

- Synthetic fixture categories.
- Allowed synthetic fields.
- Prohibited real/live/private fields.
- Fixture review checklist.
- Relationship to design-stage acceptance evidence.

